{"tid":1950564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"其實運動從來都冇靜止過. 19 歲青年賴雲龍　去年七月光復沙田襲警判罰款,律政司認為刑罰過輕上訴","createTime":"2020-03-30T11:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T11:56:11.000Z","uid":155883,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8edc2be75ae591df2657b9bad7a4ca1743af2690","tid":1950564,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/19-%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%B4%E9%9B%B2%E9%BE%8D-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE-2000-%E5%85%83-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%88%91%E7%BD%B0%E9%81%8E%E8%BC%95%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B3%25B4%25E9%259B%25B2%25E9%25BE%258D-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE-2000-%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2588%2591%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2d%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=d950431a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B3%25B4%25E9%259B%25B2%25E9%25BE%258D-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE-2000-%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2588%2591%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&h=d9196086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/19-%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%B4%E9%9B%B2%E9%BE%8D-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE-2000-%E5%85%83-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%88%91%E7%BD%B0%E9%81%8E%E8%BC%95%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4/</a><br />\n19 歲青年賴雲龍，去年 7 月 14 日在沙田以雨傘「篤」一名警長胸口，他承認一項襲警罪被判罰款 2000 元；熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰引述他的代表律師指，剛剛收到律政司來信，律政司認為刑罰過輕，正就案件判罰覆核上訴。<br />\n<br />\n賴雲龍在 2019 年 7 月 14 日，在反修例遊行後的警民衝突期間，在沙田担杆莆街襲擊警長施培佳，他認罪後判罰款 2000 元，署理主任裁判官高偉雄判刑時指，賴雲龍認為自己做的事正確，並無悔意，但考慮他主動認罪，案情不算嚴重，被告亦沒有作出侮辱行為，如向警潑液，判他罰款。<br />\n<br />\n現時賴雲龍因被控機場暴動及襲擊《環球時報》記者付國豪正在還柙，鄭松泰指律師會盡快探望他，安排處理律政司上訴。"},{"pid":"e4430c2544bdcb4207fdc51a68b4b3a7a47a823f","tid":1950564,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"付國豪中咗肺炎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}